Tab Navigation

Dummy Wats Up
API Level 21

Two Important Things Need to Know
1) ViewPager
2)TabLayout

Need to add dependencies

implementation 'com.android.support:design:28.0.0'

or
In Project Structure ->depencies->app->click on plus->library depencies ->search design 
click on ok.

Steps for Implementing the Tabs:

1)Define the tablayout using TabLayout
2)Implement a fragment and its layout for each tab.
3)Implement a PagerAdapter from FragmentPagerAdapter or Fragment State PagerAdapter
4)CreatE an instance of the tablayout.
5)Manage Screens views in Fragments
6)Set a listener to determine which tab is tapped.
